pageContext.claim: “We've created nearly 600,000 jobs in the last three months alone, think of that, 600,000, and if I ever said that, when I was campaigning, the fake news media would go, I'd say, 'Impossible.' They are fake.”
pageContext.analysis: There were 569,000 jobs created in July, August and September of 2018. In 2016, when Trump was campaigning for the presidency, there were 764,000 jobs created in July, August and September.
